France Roche https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/France_Roche 0 France Roche (2 April 1921 – 14 December 2013) was a French film actress and screenwriter. She appeared in 17 films between 1951 and 1979. She was a member of the jury at the 11th Berlin International Film Festival. France_Roche ( 2_April_1921 – 14_December_2013 ) was a_French_film_actress_and_screenwriter .
